The paper deals with deep learning for image representations and retrieval, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also uses caption generating models, which falls under natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of transfer learning and siamese networks, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with information retrieval and retrieval tasks, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
